videos.description: UCLA running back Nate Starks' three-yard touchdown run and the ensuing extra point gives UCLA a 24-23 lead with just more than three minutes remaining against BYU.
videos.headline: UCLA takes late-game lead on TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA takes late-game lead on TD) 2015/09/19 ESHEET

videos.description: UCLA linebacker Myles Jack picks off BYU quarterback Tanner Mangum in the game's final minute to preserve the Bruins' 24-23 lead.
videos.headline: Jack's interception seals UCLA win

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jack's interception seals UCLA win) 2015/09/19 ESHEET
